{"tid":2501393,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"想搵番隻好細個係電腦玩的game","createTime":"2021-04-23T10:30:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T10:40:43.000Z","uid":100860,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"39388c6750576639c339d34210d908a408c2328d","tid":2501393,"uid":100860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T10:30:15.000Z","msg":"咩名已經唔記得, 只係記得玩法好似大富翁咁係個地圖度行(但唔係買地,好似係有唔同的事發生咁)<br />\n每個人好似手上都有幾張卡(好似係有埋攻擊打幾多咁)<br />\n同埋佢d卡係好似依家d回合制game咁show哂係最下面<br />\n最緊要係記得隻game有得讀書, 唔知讀完大學之後有d特別野先做到<br />\n印象記得好似仲要打條魔龍(唔記得係咪Boss)<br />\n有成400HP跟住要用卡去打佢<br />\n可以單機多人玩或者可以加埋npc<br />\n隻game真係應該十幾年前玩過, 已經得番好小印象<br />\n有無全能的巴打可以幫手搵番隻game出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8daa45e0e4d19510d32f1976aa1fa30eda9d275","tid":2501393,"uid":349494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T10:33:11.000Z","msg":"ps2 EX人生？"},{"pid":"7e050331722b62711db1d13b813f2fd583679a5c","tid":2501393,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T10:33:18.000Z","msg":"生命之旅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7fb164f104a22abcf5342d4c948c04cce8f5fe3","tid":2501393,"uid":100860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8daa45e0e4d19510d32f1976aa1fa30eda9d275","tid":2501393,"uid":349494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T10:33:11.000Z","msg":"ps2 EX人生？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T10:40:43.000Z","msg":"唔係，佢係好似大富翁咁1人1個回合<br />\n同埋個陣係電腦同家姐佢地玩（佢地已經無哂印象）<br />\n點都好，唔該哂巴打幫手搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}